### Test Coverage Areas

1. **Shell Detection Logic**
   ```rust
   #[test]
   fn test_detect_shell_from_env() {
       std::env::set_var("SHELL", "/bin/zsh");
       assert_eq!(detect_shell(), Some(Shell::Zsh));

       std::env::set_var("SHELL", "/usr/bin/bash");
